prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: Dear diary,A close of mine died in a car crash this week. i am completely distraught because I never thought that something like this would happen to me. i thought when I saw it on the news that it was someone else. Not me by far. I thought we could go on a vacation trip because we are always working you know. This really sucks the life right out of me. That is my brother that has been there for me from the jump. This right here is going to take some time before I can recover from this. I have to question all that I know now and it hurts to do this. I love this guy because he was there when no one was there. I have to remain strong for his family but it is going to be a stretched. I have to work hard at this. Father I promise that I will make sure they are good. I wont give up on them or myself.. Give me the strength during this time. I cannot deal with this right now.

choices.text: I am just so sad and hurt. My brother is gone. I cannot believe it. I want to see him again. I want to talk to him again. I want to hear his voice again. I want to laugh with him again. I want to go on vacation with him again. I want to see him get married and have kids again. I want to see him grow old again. I want to be there for him again. I want to be there for his family again. I want to be there for my family again. This is not fair. This is not right. I cannot believe this has happened to me. I cannot believe this has happened to my family. I am so lost right now. I do not know what to do. I do not know how to feel. I do not know how to move on. I do not know how to live without him. He was my best friend. He was my rock. He was my confidant. He was my brother. He was my everything. I miss him so much. I miss him more than words can express. I miss him more than tears can shed. I miss him more than life itself. I will never be the same without him. I will never be whole
